EMAIL-SCRIPTS

This repository contains a few helper scripts for doing email with mblaze. 

https://github.com/leahneukirchen/mblaze

m - quick summary of mail (unread, by default)
ml - view, mark, and reply to mail using fzf as the interface (unread, by default)
mf - flag emails (as read, by default)
md - download attachments from an email

